      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink9">
          <l> vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> naṉṟuperitu ciṟakka tītil lākuka</l>
          <l> veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> kayalār nārai pōrviṟ cēkkun</l>
          <l> taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ kēṇmai </l>
          <l> yampalā kaṟka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>          'Long live Ātan! Long live Aviṉi! </l>
<l>          May Goodness greatly prevail! May Evil come to nought!' </l>
<l>          That's what our mother wanted. As for us: </l>
<l>          '[My] bond with the man from the village by the cool ghat,</l>
<l>          where cranes, who gorge on carp, nest on grain-heaps: </l>
<l>          May it not become [the subject of] gossip!' — that's what we want.</l>
          


        </lg>
      </div>
